											</p>


									<h3>Role of Recruitment Agency in India</h3>

									<p>The recruitment industry in India has grown rapidly. With startups and global companies expanding, recruitment companies in India are becoming a backbone of hiring.</p>
									<p>The best recruitment agency in India provides a wide range of services—placement, sourcing, RPO, and background verification. Bangalore, being a hub, has some of the strongest agencies offering recruitment agency services.</p>
